  <h2 id="opportunity-attributes-1" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">Overview</h2>
  
  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Off-payroll (IR35) determination
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Contracted out service: the off-payroll rules do not apply
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Summary of the work
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Third-party supplier to augment HO ServiceNow DevOps team with in-depth ServiceNow skills and “burst” capability. Providing ServiceNow related skills/knowledge in new/emerging areas of the platform; transfer into/establish within the in-house DevOps Team during design/delivery phases. Providing additional design, development and delivery capability to meet timescales for delivery against ServiceNow Roadmap.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Latest start date
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Monday 1 November 2021
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Expected contract length
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          24 months
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Location
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          No specific location, for example they can work remotely
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Organisation the work is for
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Secretary of State for Home Department (acting through the Home Office)
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
