          Proposal criteria
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>1.	The essential skills from stage 1</li>
          <li>2.	On-boarding and Transition</li>
          <li>3.	Approach and Methodology</li>
          <li>4.	Organisation and Sub-contractors</li>
          <li>5.     Value For Money / added value</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
